channel.title: Error: bad name or command
channel.description:
After an experience with a KEYLOGGER(I went on youtube and it had a link to rapidshare which gave me Moparscape 3.0.EXE which contained a trojan) I found the real moperscape, but when I run runMoperscape.bat(or whatever the extention is) I get this error:
[glow=red,2,300]Bad name or command[/glow]
Its in a MS-DOS window. Does anyone know a fix?
